        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "3. testified of the truth that is in thee—Greek, \"of\" (or 'to') thy truth\": thy share of that truth in which thou walkest [Alford].",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "even as thou—in contrast to Diotrephes (3Jo 9).",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Matthew Poole's Commentary",
    "elements": [
