        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2 John 1:4",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". When and why the apostle felt such a joy is stated in the two following participial sentences, of which, however, as far as the sense is concerned, the first is subordinate to the second; à Mons: lorsque les frères qui sont venus ont rendu témoignage.",
        "children": []
