      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). The whole, literally rendered, runs thus; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "For I rejoiced greatly at brethren coming and witnessing to thy truth",
